      </div>

      <div class="cap-grid">
        <a class="cap-card reveal reveal-delay-1" href="/platforms">
          <div class="cap-card-photo" style="background-image:url('/photos/card-home-site-selection.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="cap-card-body">
            <div class="cap-num">01 — Site</div>
            <h3 class="cap-title">Site Selection</h3>
            <p class="cap-desc">Score LatAm cities by land, grid, water and fiscal.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="cap-card reveal reveal-delay-2" href="/platforms">
          <div class="cap-card-photo" style="background-image:url('/photos/card-home-grid-intel.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="cap-card-body">
            <div class="cap-num">02 — Grid</div>
            <h3 class="cap-title">Grid Intelligence</h3>
            <p class="cap-desc">508 ONS studies. PARPEL 2027–2031. Reports in 24h.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="cap-card reveal reveal-delay-1" href="/platforms">
          <div class="cap-card-photo" style="background-image:url('/photos/card-home-dc-financial.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="cap-card-body">
            <div class="cap-num">03 — Capital</div>
            <h3 class="cap-title">DC Financial Model</h3>
            <p class="cap-desc">TCO + IRR with country tariffs and FX stress.</p>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a class="cap-card reveal reveal-delay-2" href="/platforms">
          <div class="cap-card-photo" style="background-image:url('/photos/card-home-testfit-pro.jpg');"></div>
          <div class="cap-card-body">
            <div class="cap-num">04 — Fit-out</div>
