  <section class="principles on-cream">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="reveal" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom: 24px;">
        <div class="section-eyebrow" style="justify-content:center;">How we work</div>
        <h2 class="section-heading" style="margin: 0 auto; max-width: 680px;">Three principles. <span class="blue">Non-negotiable.</span></h2>
      </div>
      <div class="principles-grid reveal reveal-delay-1" style="margin-top: 64px;">
        <div class="principle">
          <div class="principle-num">01</div>
          <h4>Primary sources only</h4>
          <p>Every claim links to a document we can hand a regulator.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle">
          <div class="principle-num">02</div>
          <h4>Partners on every call</h4>
          <p>The person who builds the memo presents it. No pyramid.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="principle">
          <div class="principle-num">03</div>
          <h4>Audited before delivery</h4>
          <p>Chain of Truth review. If we can't verify, we drop it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="insight" id="intelligence">
    <div class="insight-inner">
      <div class="insight-img reveal">
        <div class="insight-img-bg" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        <span class="insight-tag">Memo 011 · Live</span>
        <div class="insight-stat-overlay">
          <span><strong class="blue">8</strong>Substations mapped</span>
          <span><strong>+18 GW</strong>Headroom identified</span>
          <span><strong>2028</strong>Operative cycle</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">Latest research</div>
        <h3>Where Brazil's 2028 grid headroom <span class="blue">actually sits</span> — and why Vespasiano matters more than Uberlândia.</h3>
        <p>PARPEL Cycle 2027–2031 cross-referenced with N-1 contingency across four target sites. The operative capacity story is being mispriced. We map the eight substations that change the math.</p>
        <div class="insight-meta">
          <span><strong>Memo 011</strong>Power · Brazil</span>
          <span><strong>14 pages</strong>7 primary sources</span>
          <span><strong>May 2026</strong>Members only</span>
        </div>
        <a href="/intelligence" class="insight-cta" aria-label="Read memo 011">
          Read memo
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M1 7h12M7 1l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

